The paper deals with the formalization of data deletion, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The use of cryptography tools and paradigms suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG), as cryptography is often used in secure machine learning applications. The paper also discusses data processing systems, which is a topic that falls under the category of databases (cs.DB). The discussion of technological solutions suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of cybernetics (cs.CY) and software engineering (cs.SE).
